ZH: 1. 人行道旁边种了很多树。
EN: There are many trees planted beside the sidewalk.
ZH: 2. 小心，人行道上有很多坑洼。
EN: Be careful, there are many potholes on the sidewalk.
ZH: 3. 这条人行道已经修好了。
EN: This sidewalk has been repaired.
ZH: 4. 孩子们在人行道上骑着自行车。
EN: The children are riding their bicycles on the sidewalk.
ZH: 5. 请保持人行道整洁。
EN: Please keep the sidewalk clean.
ZH: 6. 人行道上有很多人在散步。
EN: There are many people walking on the sidewalk.
ZH: 7. 他摔倒在人行道上受伤了。
EN: He fell on the sidewalk and got injured.
ZH: 8. 这条人行道通往公园。
EN: This sidewalk leads to the park.
ZH: 9. 她沿着人行道慢慢地走过去。
EN: She walked slowly along the sidewalk.
ZH: 10. 人行道前面有一个红绿灯。
EN: There is a traffic light in front of the sidewalk.
ZH: 11. 这条人行道很宽，可以容纳很多人。
EN: This sidewalk is wide enough to accommodate many people.
ZH: 12. 请勿在人行道上乱扔垃圾。
EN: Please do not litter on the sidewalk.
ZH: 13. 人行道上有很多商店和餐馆。
EN: There are many shops and restaurants on the sidewalk.
ZH: 14. 他们正沿着人行道奔跑着。
EN: They are running along the sidewalk.
ZH: 15. 这条人行道可以供行人和自行车共享。
EN: This sidewalk is for pedestrians and bicycles to share.
ZH: 16. 她从人行道的另一边走过来。
EN: She walked from the other side of the sidewalk.
ZH: 17. 这条人行道非常狭窄，只能容纳一人通过。
EN: This sidewalk is very narrow, only one person can pass at a time.
ZH: 18. 人行道上有很多滑溜溜的积水。
EN: There are many slippery puddles on the sidewalk.
ZH: 19. 他们在人行道上画了一幅彩色的画。
EN: They painted a colorful picture on the sidewalk.
ZH: 20. 人行道上有很多人排队等候。
EN: There are many people queuing on the sidewalk.
